HEADWORD: Luckily
<hw>Luck"i*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Lucky</er>.]</ety> <def>In a lucky manner; by good fortune;
fortunately; -- used in a good sense; <as>as, they <ex>luckily</ex>
escaped injury</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Luckiness</ent>⟦br⟧
